      • LicenceNumber

        public LicenceNumber(java.lang.String first,
                     int second,
                     int third)
        Construct a licence number from the given first, second and last.
        参数:
        first - the first component of the licence number.
        second - the second component of the licence number.
        third - the third component of the licence number.
        抛出:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if either first, second or third is null
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if either first, second or third is empty

      • toString

        public java.lang.String toString()
        Returns a string representation of a licence number. The string representation is a first part, second part and third part separated by a "-" signal.
        覆盖:
        toString 在类中 java.lang.Object
        另请参阅:
        Object.toString(), for the string representation of a licence number.

      • valueOf

        public static LicenceNumber valueOf(java.lang.String licenceNumber)
        Constructs an instance of LicenceNumber from its string representation. The string representation is a first part, second part and third part separated by a "-" signal.
        参数:
        licenceNumber - a licence number in the specified string representation
        返回:
        an instance of a LicenceNumber corresponding to the given string
        抛出:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if licenceNumber is null
        java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException - if there are not three component parts to licenceNumber (first, second and third parts)
